ğŸ“– Overview

This project explores cyber attack trends across industries such as finance, healthcare, government, IT, and energy.
The objective is to identify:

Which sectors are most frequently targeted

Year-wise changes in cyber attack intensity

Common attack types affecting each industry

The analysis was performed in Python using Jupyter Notebook, with data visualization to highlight key insights.

ğŸ“Š Dataset

Source: Publicly available cyber attack dataset:-  Kaggle

Format: CSV file with columns:

Year

Sector

Number_of_Attacks

Attack_Type 

ğŸ“Œ Dataset file: data/cyber_incidents.csv

